sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Publisher<br/>(センサー)
    participant B as Broker
    participant S1 as Subscriber A<br/>(ダッシュボード)
    participant S2 as Subscriber B<br/>(ログ収集)

    Note over S1,S2: 1. サブスクライバーがトピックを購読
    S1->>B: SUBSCRIBE "sensor/temp"
    B->>S1: SUBACK (成功)
    S2->>B: SUBSCRIBE "sensor/temp"
    B->>S2: SUBACK (成功)

    Note over P,B: 2. パブリッシャーがメッセージを発行
    P->>B: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "25.3"

    Note over B,S2: 3. ブローカーが購読者に配信
    B->>S1: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "25.3"
    B->>S2: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "25.3"

    Note over P,B: 4. 別のメッセージを発行
    P->>B: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "26.1"
    B->>S1: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "26.1"
    B->>S2: PUBLISH "sensor/temp"<br/>payload = "26.1"
